text: If you looking for lively market with numerous stalls & hawkers offering seafood & local specialities (halal food provided for muslim)..this is the right place for you with family and friends. Open daily from 12pm to 2am

Was disappointed by the time I had to wait for the bus, and ended up having to call a cab because I was late for my appointment although I came out earlier than I normally will. The inconsistency of 3 bus, 10mins apart, was just mind boggling.
